{"article_id":"ZwDm5FoELD08ldux","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Some Republicans are livid","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that Sulaiman Abu Ghaith , the son-in-law of Osama bin Laden , is facing a civilian trial","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"- instead of a military trial .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"They see this as a political move","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"intended to build a case","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"for closing the US military prison in Guantanamo , Cuba .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"President Barack Obama has said","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"that he wants more foreign terror suspects charged in American federal courts , not in military tribunals at Guantanamo .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Abu Ghaith pleaded 'not guilty ' in an arraignment in New York City Friday morning .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"His trial will be a high-profile case , a rare prosecution of a senior Al Qaeda leader in under US civil law .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"But Republicans do n't want foreign terrorists tried on US soil .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"They say","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"the legal precedent has been set for `` enemy combatants '' to be tried at Guantanamo Bay .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"They are concerned","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that giving Abu Ghaith a civilian trial will result in lost intelligence .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Sen. Kelly Ayotte","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"( R of N.H. )","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"told reporters","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"by bringing Ghaith to New York ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"he would be entitled to the same rights as a citizen ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"including a speedy trial and Miranda rights ,","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"according to Politico .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"\" We do n't want him to come to America","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"before he has been fully interrogated -","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"before he comes to America","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"and hears the words , ' You have the right","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"to remain silent . ' \" `` We believe","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"the administration 's decision here","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"to bring this person to New York City ,","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"if that 's what 's happened ,","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"without letting Congress know","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"is a very bad precedent","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"to set , ''","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"said Sen. Lindsey Graham ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"( R of S.C. )","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"in a press conference Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Senator Ayotte also told reporters","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"`` When we find somebody like this , this close to bin Laden and the senior Al Qaeda leadership ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"the last thing","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"in the world","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"we want to do ,","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"in my opinion , is put them in civilian court .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"This man should be in Guantanamo Bay . ''","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"`` So we 're putting the administration on notice , ''","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Senator Graham said .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"`` We think","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that sneaking this guy into the country ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"clearly going around the intent of Congress","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"when it comes to enemy combatants ,","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"will be challenged . ''","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":55,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"In a statement on the website of the US Attorney for the Southern District of New York , FBI Assistant Director-in-Charge George Venizelos described Sulaiman Abu Ghayth as holding `` a key position in al Qaeda , comparable to the consigliere in a mob family or propaganda minister in a totalitarian regime .","depth":4},{"id":58,"text":"He used his position","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"to persuade others to swear loyalty to al Qaeda ' s murderous cause .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"He used his position","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"to threaten the United States","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"and incite its enemies .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"His apprehension is another important step in the campaign","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"to limit the reach of al Qaeda","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"and enhance our national and international security . \"","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"On the morning of September 12 , 2001 , Abu Ghayth , appeared with Bin Laden and Zawahiri ,","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"and spoke on behalf of al Qaeda ,","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"warning the United States and its allies","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that \" [ a ] great army is gathering against you \"","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"and called upon \" the nation of Islam \" to do battle against \" the Jews , the Christians and the Americans. \"","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Also , after the September 11 , 2001 terrorist attacks , Abu Ghayth delivered a speech","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"in which he addressed the then-US Secretary of State","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"and warned","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that \" the storms shall not stop , especially the Airplanes Storm , \"","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"and advised Muslims , children , and opponents of the United States \" not to board any aircraft","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"and not to live in high rises . \"","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"The indictment charges Abu Ghayth with participating in a conspiracy","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"to kill United States nationals ,","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"in violation of Title 18 , United States Code , Section 2332 ( b ) .","depth":4},{"id":80,"text":"The offense carries a maximum term of imprisonment for life .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":161,"left":137,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":132,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":88,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":86,"right":87,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":83,"right":85,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":0,"right":82,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":82,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":3,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":89,"right":130,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":89,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":130,"left":93,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":10,"right":92,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":90,"right":91,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":129,"left":114,"right":128,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":114,"left":100,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":95,"right":99,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":94,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":18,"right":97,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":97,"left":19,"righ